    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It's in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and drives like a dream! I've taken great care of it over the years, so it's ready to hit the road for its next adventure. If you're looking for something reliable that still looks fantastic and feels great to drive, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
