      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque delivery across the rev range. This chassis benefits from a factory-equipped limited-slip differential and has undergone a recent suspension refresh with polyurethane bushings to sharpen turn-in response. Crucial maintenance items have been addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive subframe inspection for structural integrity. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina consistent with its use, the mechanical synchronicity and throttle mapping remain sharp, offering an authentic analog driving experience.",
